{{Relic Infobox|Touch of Orobas|2}}
{{R|Touch of Orobas||2}} is an {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Ancient|Ancient|2}} {{2|Relics|Relic}}. Upon pickup, it replaces your {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Starter|Starter Relic|2}} with an upgraded version.

== Obtaining Touch of Orobas ==
At the start of {{2|Acts#Act 2|Act 2|2}}, can be offered by {{KW|Orobas||2}}.

== Notes ==
The upgraded {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Starter|Starter Relics|2}} you can obtain are as follows:
* '''Ironclad''': {{R|Burning Blood||2}} -> {{R|Black Blood||2}}
* '''Silent''': {{R|Ring of the Snake||2}} -> {{R|Ring of the Drake||2}}
* '''Regent''': {{R|Divine Right||2}} -> {{R|Divine Destiny||2}}
* '''Necrobinder''': {{R|Bound Phylactery||2}} -> {{R|Phylactery Unbound||2}}
* '''Defect''': {{R|Cracked Core||2}} -> {{R|Infused Core||2}}

== Trivia ==
*Although the description in the in-game Compendium says it replaces your {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Starter|Starter Relic|2}} with an {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Ancient|Ancient|2}} version, the rarities of the upgraded {{2|Relics}} are shown as {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Starter|Starter|2}}.

